imdb.title: Dolls' Frontline
imdb.plot: In a world where female androids have become a new military weapon to use, a squad is tasked to hunt down any girls who have rebelled and turned on humanity.

episodes.title: The Seed
episodes.plot: Elite T-Dolls infiltrate an abandoned "recon command post". But, they immediately learn that the opposing forces have been waiting with their agents; they, too, want the secret data the T-Dolls are after.

episodes.title: Wake Up
episodes.plot: Commander Gentiane is invited into the base to begin her mission. But, why must she interrogate the T-Dolls first before commencing her duties?

episodes.title: The Echo
episodes.plot: A recovery mission, the Scarecrow scare, a mole within the PMC, and an Executioner. With everything going haywire, will a meet-up between M4A1 and the Executioner spark an alliance or a rift?

episodes.title: Silence01
episodes.plot: The T-Dolls and M4 had a secret meeting with Commander Gentiane regarding a rescue operation. Will the Griffin T-Dolls' antique weapons win against SF more advanced weaponry?
